#. <section class="sutta" id="sn23.9"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn23.9:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 23"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 23"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn23.9:0.2"
msgid "1. Paṭhamamāravagga"
msgstr "1. About Māra"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn23.9:0.3"
msgid "9. Chandarāgasutta"
msgstr "9. Desire and Greed"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.194"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn23.9:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn23.9:1.2"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho āyasmantaṃ rādhaṃ bhagavā etadavoca:"
msgstr "When Venerable Rādha was seated to one side, the Buddha said to him:"

#. </p><p class="added">
msgctxt "sn23.9:1.3"
msgid "“rūpe kho, rādha, yo chando yo rāgo yā nandī yā taṇhā, taṃ pajahatha."
msgstr "“Rādha, you should give up any desire, greed, relishing, and craving for form."

msgctxt "sn23.9:1.4"
msgid "Evaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ pahīnaṃ bhavissati ucchinnamūlaṃ tālāvatthukataṃ anabhāvaṅkataṃ āyatiṃ anuppādadhammaṃ."
msgstr "Thus that form will be given up, cut off at the root, made like a palm stump, obliterated, and unable to arise in the future."

msgctxt "sn23.9:1.5"
msgid "Vedanāya yo chando yo rāgo yā nandī yā taṇhā, taṃ pajahatha."
msgstr "You should give up any desire, greed, relishing, and craving for feeling …"

msgctxt "sn23.9:1.6"
msgid "Evaṃ sā vedanā pahīnā bhavissati ucchinnamūlā tālāvatthukatā anabhāvaṅkatā āyatiṃ anuppādadhammā."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn23.9:1.7"
msgid "Saññāya …"
msgstr "perception …"

msgctxt "sn23.9:1.8"
msgid "saṅkhāresu yo chando yo rāgo yā nandī yā taṇhā, taṃ pajahatha."
msgstr "choices …"

msgctxt "sn23.9:1.9"
msgid "Evaṃ te saṅkhārā pahīnā bhavissanti ucchinnamūlā tālāvatthukatā anabhāvaṅkatā āyatiṃ anuppādadhammā."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn23.9:1.10"
msgid "Viññāṇe yo chando yo rāgo yā nandī yā taṇhā, taṃ pajahatha."
msgstr "consciousness."

msgctxt "sn23.9:1.11"
msgid "Evaṃ taṃ viññāṇaṃ pahīnaṃ bhavissati … pe … anuppādadhamman”ti."
msgstr "Thus that consciousness will be given up, cut off at the root, made like a palm stump, obliterated, and unable to arise in the future.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn23.9:1.12"
msgid "Navamaṃ."
msgstr ""
